    "body": "Out of all the options, I think I prefer 'automatic ping'. Exposing the connection is messy because of the automatic reconnect. Exposing a `Ping` method is weird because it would only work on WebSocket.\r\n\r\nI'm not 100% what the best way to implement this would be. We can probably fit the ping into client by starting an additional background goroutine when opening the websocket connection.",
